short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Integrates Rate My Professor with Austin Community College's Self Service page.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Rate My Professor, for ACC makes searching for good professors at Austin Community College easier, by integrating professors' Rate My Professor reviews with ACC's Self service page.

Whenever you search for courses through ACC's Self Service site, this extension will add a little widget next to each professor's name, with their Rate My Professor rating. You can click on the widget to view more info about the professor or look at their reviews, and open their corresponding Rate My Professor page.
